<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <% include ./partials/head %>
</head>
<body class="container">
<header>
    <% include ./partials/header %>
</header>
<div class="panel panel-default" style="margin-top: 3%;">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
            <h1 class="text-center">DEBAT N°1</h1>

            <div class="thumbnail">
                <img src="../images/clinton-trump.jpg" alt="Clinton Trump">
                <div class="caption">
                    <h3>Pour ou contre ajouter la dimension des émotions dans un débat sur internet ? (dans le cadre de notre projet)</h3>
                    <div>
                        <form id="deb" action="/chat/debate" method="POST">
                            <a href="#" id="debate" type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-primary">Participer</a>
                            <input type="hidden" name="room" value="debate">
                            <input type="hidden" name="pseudo" value="<%- pseudo %>">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
            <h1 class="text-center">DEBAT N°2</h1>
            <div class="thumbnail" >
                <img src="../images/global-warming.jpg" alt="Global Warming">
                <div class="caption">
                    <h3>Est-ce que le remplacement des partiels à Polytech par des contrôles continus est une bonne idée ?</h3>
                    <div>
                        <form id="env" action="/chat/gw" method="POST">
                            <a href="#" id="gw" type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-primary">Participer</a>
                            <input type="hidden" name="room" value="gw">
                            <input type="hidden" name="pseudo" value="<%- pseudo %>">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<footer>
    <% include ./partials/footer.ejs %>
</footer>
</body>
</html>

<!-- HOME PAGE RETURN SCRIPT -->
<script>
    $("#debate").click(function () {
        $("#deb").submit();
    });

    $("#gw").click(function () {
        $("#env").submit();
    });

</script>

<!-- HOME PAGE RETURN SCRIPT -->
<script>
    $("#home").click(function () {
        window.location.href = "https://ceihm-emotions.herokuapp.com/lobby/<%- pseudo %>"
    });
</script>